track.description: David returns after holiday to chat with Scot about the Gers up-and-down start to the season and the summer signings. They also chat about General Franco, how to control a journalist through a fist/bottom interface, President Obama's codename and quite possibly the stupidest football fan of all time. Yes, he supports the other lot.
